  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Araucaria Hotel &amp; Spa is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each morning fuel up for the day at the extensive breakfast buffet which includes a classic continental offering, as well as daily hot options. Breakfast is served between <span>07:00 to 10:00, room service is offered until 11:00.</span></p>
<p>When you return from a day on the slopes a varied buffet style dinner with different themed stations awaits - there is something for everyone. There are two seating's, the first from<span> 6:45pm to 8:15 and the later sitting served from 8:15pm to 9:15pm. </span></p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
