  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are around 17m² sleeping two people <span>with a double bed or two single beds. Most of these rooms have their own private balcony. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy on request, please give our Reservations team a call to book.</span></p>
<p><strong>Superior Room</strong> are around 24m² sleeping two to three people<span> with a double bed and a single bed or three single beds. The a</span>dditional single bed is suitable for a child up to 12 years old. </p>
<p>Interconnecting rooms are available on request. Please note that baby cots are not possible in Classic rooms.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Kettle</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment</li>
<li>Bathrobe &amp; slippers</li>
<li>Welcome products</li>
<li>Baby cots are available on request (book in advance - free of charge)</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
